      "content": "That's a bit of a vague answer lol. Like, when people talk about the stats, isn't there basically a consensus that more guns = more violence? And and on the legal side, doesn't the Supreme Court pretty much settle the constitutionality part, making the \"debate\" kind of a moot point?",
